:09.000Z","msg":"東德先係"},{"pid":"58a8203a80f5dcffd8918ead70662ac44b397beb","tid":741142,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T02:14:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67d4649a75acaff7866cf1e6d6bb21794e8b3e00","tid":741142,"uid":42283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T02:19:15.000Z","msg":"德國戰後復與七十年幾年毀係個垃圾總理手上<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afbbf020befe4af005366f3828df09fe7b641614","tid":741142,"uid":41382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T02:20:35.000Z","msg":"中俄德新軸心國"},{"pid":"e7e0a7c2b2071b44df353d4065dd4490bb431f67","tid":741142,"uid":109462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T02:25:09.000Z","msg":"默克爾真係功過五五開，甚至最近已經係過大於功。<br />\n<br />\n默克爾以前面對歐洲經濟危機領導有方，功在當代；但難民政策一塌糊塗，如今又受中共蒙蔽，令中共自西安事變後再次絕處逢生，可謂禍在千秋。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}